# Platform — Hotsite Manifest (public)
# M12-S01: HotsiteConfig domain + manifest API
# Reached via BFF GET /v1/platform/manifest/:slug → getForPublic('/hotsite', tenantId)
# TenantContext is populated from X-Tenant-ID (set by the BFF). No actor required.
#
# Prerequisites:
#   1. pnpm infra:up
#   2. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run migration:run
#   3. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run dev
#
# REST Client environment: select "local" in VS Code status bar

@baseUrl = {{backendUrl}}
@internalKey = {{$dotenv INTERNAL_API_KEY}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HAPPY PATH
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get the published hotsite manifest for a tenant
GET {{baseUrl}}/hotsite
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-Internal-Key: {{internalKey}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ERROR CASES
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 400 — Missing X-Tenant-ID header
GET {{baseUrl}}/hotsite

###

### 404 — Hotsite is not published (or no config exists yet for the tenant)
GET {{baseUrl}}/hotsite
X-Tenant-ID: 00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000009999
